---

<section class="testimonials">
  <h2 class="section-title">Testimonials</h2>
  <div class="testimonials-list">
    <blockquote class="testimonial">
      <p>“Ajam consistently demonstrates strong analytical skills and a deep understanding of seismic data processing. His contributions to our EEWS project were invaluable.”</p>
      <footer>— Dr. Budi Santoso, Geoseismal Research Center</footer>
    </blockquote>
    <blockquote class="testimonial">
      <p>“Ajam’s ability to mentor and communicate complex concepts made a significant impact on our students’ learning outcomes.”</p>
      <footer>— Dr. Siti Rahmawati, Universitas Gadjah Mada</footer>
